dct_description_sm: [Lancashire] County Planning Council. County Planning and Development Committee. Companion text: A Preliminary Plan for Lancashire / Gerald William Sutton Brown. Preston: Lancashire County Council. County Planning and Development Committee. 1952. 222p. [With three maps, each in four sections.]. Inset: Furness area (on sheet two). Legend: A/2, 1951. "Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the sanction of H.M. Stationery Office." The Map Library lacks the accompanying text.
dct_publisher_sm: Lancashire (England) : County Planning and Development Committee., [1951].
